<p align="center">
  Tech Lead building <b>high-load, distributed services</b> in <b>Python</b> &amp; <b>Go</b>.<br/>
  Hands-on with <b>databases (internals &amp; tuning)</b>, <b>Kubernetes</b>, <b>Docker</b> and <b>observability</b>;
  designing systems for scale and reliability.<br/>
  Currently going deeper into <b>ML &amp; LangChain</b>, and shipping the occasional <b>React / Next.js</b> frontend.<br/>
  I also write about backend engineering on <a href="https://habr.com/ru/users/andy-takker/">Habr</a>.
</p>


